Pubertal_onset.description: Computed using physician observed Tanner response TN15_1, TN15_2 and TN15_3. Pubertal onset = 0 if both TN15_1 and TN15_2 for female (or TN15_1 and TN15_3 for male) is 1. Pubertal onset = 1 if either TN15_1 or TN15_2 for female (or TN15_1 and TN15_3 for male) is greater than 1
